It’s official!  Tickets for The Battle For The Bay are now on sale!

We can’t wait to see everyone in Tampa for this afternoon of baseball and family fun! All proceeds go to the Alonso Foundation as we focus on creating healthy outlets for the youth of our community.

Come out to see some MLB friends hit some bombs at Plant High School. 🎟️ link in bio & @alonsofoundation

Couldn’t be more thrilled to introduce you all to Bear! @alonsofoundation sponsored the training of Bear through @K9sForWarriors to be partnered with a veteran in need of a service dog. Bear will be with us at #BattleForTheBay in Tampa on 1/14, and we are so proud of all the hard work he’s been putting in learning how to support a veteran in need. Come on out to Plant HS next Saturday to see Bear and the Polar Bear!
Battle For The Bay is on!!! Saturday 1/14 3pm-6pm at Plant High School. Check out link in bio tickets or visit AlonsoFoundation.org

Battle For The Bay was an absolute blast!! It was amazing bringing the baseball and softball communities of Tampa together along with @ktuck_30 arroyoc22 @urshela10 @cpena23. Special thanks to @sportstampabay @mlb @mlbnetwork and our sponsors: @citibank @nikediamond @fanatics @topps @pdqfreshfood @kenny_hwang_nyc @dugoutmugs @mcmag_difference @miracletoyotafl #CNAinsurance @perfectgameusa @wear_riot @collegehunkstampa @the_datavault @bigtimebats @oaicorp

#ServiceDog Bear met his fam @polarpete20 & @haleyralonso @ the Battle For The Bay last weekend. With the help of the @alonsofoundation, Bear will be paired with a veteran suffering from #PTSD. Catch him at spring training w/the boys. ⚾

The NY Mets' star @mets and two-time Home Run Derby champion Pete Alonso @polarpete20 joins us this week on Plákata Nation Podcast to share his work ethic, the foundation of his powerful swing, his thoughts on Aaron Judge, and his commitment to the communities of New York and Tampa. Enjoy it with Spanish subtitles on our Youtube channel. PLÁKATA!

La estrella de @losmets y 2 veces campeón del Home Run Derby Pete Alonso, nos acompaña esta semana en Plákata Nation Podcast para compartir su ética de trabajo, la base de su poderoso swing, su opinión sobre Aaron Judge, y su compromiso con las comunidades de New York y Tampa. Disfrútalo con subtítulos en español en nuestro canal de Youtube.

¡Plákata! #NYMets #LosMets #PolarPete #PeteAlonso #TheAlonsoFoundation #HomeRunDerby #SubwaySeries #AaronJudge #LasMayores
Happy Valentine’s Day to the love of my life 😍 Life is the best with you in it. It’s truly a blessing you’re my forever Valentine 😘
Feels good to be back #LFGM

The WBC was such an incredible experience. It was an honor being able to represent the US with my fellow Mets and also meet and play with some of the best players in the game!!!! Such a wild ride. Until next time WBC ✌🏻
Man it’s good to be home!!! Great team win to start the home stand! Huge shout out to all the people who came out for the home opener #LFGM
What a series win!!! Off to the west coast #LFGM

Had a blast out on the water back in my hometown in Tampa with @Columbia1938 and @CaptainsforCleanWater. We were out in the bay talking about the importance of protecting my home state of Florida’s and its waterways! The work @captainsforclearwater is doing back in Florida is crucial to our state and please give them a follow and support their mission. Thank you to Columbia PFG for their support in this initiative @alonsofoundation. See more at WatchStadium.com/Columbia #ad
#LFGM Feels good to join the #CandyFam! Go follow @candydigital for a chance to win my signed jersey and get in on some 🔥 collectibles this season 🤙🏻
Today is Mental Health Awareness Day. Mental health is important and you are not alone.

Like baseball, fishing requires skill and the right equipment. To stay cool and protected on the water, I always choose Columbia PFG. Check out my latest convo with @captainsforcleanwater where we dive deep into my two passions - baseball and fishing. See more at WatchStadium.com/Columbia and gear up for your season at Columbia.com/PFG #ad #ColumbiaPFG #baseball #mets #fishing

Don’t forget to post your Pete-inspired pics with #VoteForPete All participants will also be entered to win great prizes. Link to first clue is in the bio!
See your squad represented in Seattle 🌟 #VoteMets at the link in bio!

I’m so excited to turn a half hearted day dream/promise into a reality. I was taking batting practice 15 years ago in Tampa, FL at 13 years old. Now we can do the same thing in a few days in Seattle. Despite there being people watching in a big stadium with way more watching on tv, it’s still the same thing. Batting practice with coach Mike

This season was a wild ride. I wish we could have been the last team standing, but the baseball gods will reward hard work and determination sometime in the future. Despite everything, I couldn’t do what I do without my wife and my rock by my side every day and night ♥️ 2024 is a going to be a year of high aspirations and positive manifestations coming into fruition. #LFGM

When I’m not playing baseball, I love getting outside and fishing and hunting. It’s part of who I am and what makes this country great. The Theodore Roosevelt Conservation Partnership (TRCP) is working to make sure all Americans have quality places to hunt and fish. To support TRCP’s great work, and my work through the Alonso Foundation, enter TRCP’s Fall Sweepstakes to win an all-expenses paid trip for two in January or February to fish with me on Tampa Bay.

Click the link on my story to enter! Also, the link is in my bio!

Enter today and I’ll see you on the water this winter.
